    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my trusty ride and it\u2019s honestly such a great find. It\u2019s been super reliable for me and is still in really solid shape, just looking for its next adventure! It drives like a dream and has been well cared for over the years. Perfect for anyone looking for a dependable car without the brand-new price tag. Come take it for a spin\u2014you\u2019re gonna love it!",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
