      "description": "We are pleased to present this meticulously maintained vehicle, representing an exceptional balance of proven performance and long-term value. This unit has undergone a comprehensive multi-point inspection to ensure mechanical integrity and aesthetic consistency. Featuring a well-preserved interior and a robust powertrain, it offers a refined driving experience for the discerning owner. A premier choice for those seeking a reliable, high-caliber vehicle that stands as a testament to diligent previous ownership.",
      "price": 34500.0,
