      "description": "This 2004 BMW M3 (E46) is a driver-spec example featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine with individual throttle bodies and Double VANOS variable valve timing. Power is delivered through a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission to the rear wheels via a factory M-Variable limited-slip differential. The chassis has been maintained for performance, including documented rear subframe reinforcement and refreshed suspension bushings to ensure precise handling dynamics. Recent mechanical service includes a valve clearance adjustment and rod bearing inspection, confirming the powertrain is ready for the redline. Finished in Carbon Black with a well-preserved Nappa leather interior, this E46 offers a pure analog connection to the road.",
